cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper discusses a deep learning architecture (Ladder Network) and its components, and presents an extensive experimental investigation of variants of the architecture. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. The paper also uses the architecture for image classification tasks (cs.CV), and discusses its applications in semi-supervised learning (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
